{"tid":2207853,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"怒海之後: 12 港人送中案全紀錄專頁","createTime":"2020-09-18T12:18:14.000Z","updateTime":"2020-09-19T23:13:41.000Z","uid":240362,"like":12,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":16,"replies":[{"pid":"f7e5dcf6aea9076ab63f25646e051c68e2d45082","tid":2207853,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-18T12:18:14.000Z","msg":"12 名港人在 8 月 23 日疑在潛逃台灣中途，被中國海警截獲，內地執法機關以涉嫌非法入境内地（偷越國境罪），拘留 12 人，至今 27 天。年齡介乎 16 至 33 歲，當中包括被指違反《國安法》的「香港故事」成員李宇軒。12 人裡，大部分在香港被控不同刑事罪行，正保釋候審，11 人遭香港法庭頒令不准離港，當中 10 人被通緝。<br />\n<br />\n據報他們當日早上約六時，從西貢布袋澳碼頭乘坐快艇出發。數小時後，在 70 公里外的位置被中國海警截獲，送到深圳市鹽田看守所。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.thestandnews.com/politics/%E6%80%92%E6%B5%B7%E4%B9%8B%E5%BE%8C-12-%E6%B8%AF%E4%BA%BA%E9%80%81%E4%B8%AD%E6%A1%88%E5%85%A8%E7%B4%80%E9%8C%84%E5%B0%88%E9%A0%81/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thestandnews.com%2Fpolitics%2F%25E6%2580%2592%25E6%25B5%25B7%25E4%25B9%258B%25E5%25BE%258C-12-%25E6%25B8%25AF%25E4%25BA%25BA%25E9%2580%2581%25E4%25B8%25AD%25E6%25A1%2588%25E5%2585%25A8%25E7%25B4%2580%25E9%258C%2584%25E5%25B0%2588%25E9%25A0%2581%2F&d=U3in%2BbByR8w%2FZmejrHnAdZKhd8YmQljH21R%2F5cbT5WU%3D&h=f61a4859\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thestandnews.com%2Fpolitics%2F%25E6%2580%2592%25E6%25B5%25B7%25E4%25B9%258B%25E5%25BE%258C-12-%25E6%25B8%25AF%25E4%25BA%25BA%25E9%2580%2581%25E4%25B8%25AD%25E6%25A1%2588%25E5%2585%25A8%25E7%25B4%2580%25E9%258C%2584%25E5%25B0%2588%25E9%25A0%2581%2F&h=e6342926\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.thestandnews.com/politics/%E6%80%92%E6%B5%B7%E4%B9%8B%E5%BE%8C-12-%E6%B8%AF%E4%BA%BA%E9%80%81%E4%B8%AD%E6%A1%88%E5%85%A8%E7%B4%80%E9%8C%84%E5%B0%88%E9%A0%81/</a>"},{"pid":"1a9fe7df6ea23f1ed37c38631bf44866c0972363","tid":2207853,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-18T12:19:30.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" clas